blogPost.excerpt: Join us for the first-ever livestream for young Americans before and during the Inaugural Ceremonies. The livestream, hosted by award-winning entertainer and advocate Keke Palmer, will feature a special message from Dr. Jill Biden; commentary from historians Doris Kearns Goodwin and Erica Armstrong Dunbar; a segment on presidential pets produced by Nickelodeon; excerpts of student voices from PBS NewsHour Student Reporting Labs “We the Young People” programming; trivia questions, including some asked by Doug Emhoff; segments produced by the Library of Congress; and other special features.
blogPost.body: Join us for the first-ever livestream for young Americans before and during the Inaugural Ceremonies. The livestream, hosted by award-winning entertainer and advocate Keke Palmer, will feature a special message from Dr. Jill Biden; commentary from historians Doris Kearns Goodwin and Erica Armstrong Dunbar; a segment on presidential pets produced by Nickelodeon; excerpts of student voices from PBS NewsHour Student Reporting Labs “We the Young People” programming; trivia questions, including some asked by Doug Emhoff; segments produced by the Library of Congress; and other special features.
blogPost.title: Our White House: An Inaugural Celebration for Young Americans hosted by Keke Palmer
blogPost.author: Biden Inaugural Committee

localize.title: 我们的白宫。美国年轻人的就职庆典，由Keke Palmer主持。
localize.description: 在就职典礼之前和期间，加入我们，参加有史以来第一次为美国年轻人举办的直播。视频直播由屡获殊荣的艺人和倡导者Keke Palmer主持，将播放Jill Biden博士的特别致辞；历史学家Doris Kearns Goodwin和Erica Armstrong Dunbar的评论；Nickelodeon公司制作的关于总统宠物的片段；PBS NewsHour学生报道实验室 "我们年轻人 "节目中学生的声音摘录；包括Doug Emhoff提出的一些小问题；国会图书馆制作的片段；以及其他特别节目。

localize.title: 我們的白宮。美國年輕人的就職慶典，由Keke Palmer主持。
localize.description: 在就職典禮之前和期間，加入我們，參加有史以來第一次爲美國年輕人舉辦的直播。視頻直播由屢獲殊榮的藝人和倡導者Keke Palmer主持，將播放Jill Biden博士的特別緻辭；歷史學家Doris Kearns Goodwin和Erica Armstrong Dunbar的評論；Nickelodeon公司製作的關於總統寵物的片段；PBS NewsHour學生報道實驗室 "我們年輕人 "節目中學生的聲音摘錄；包括Doug Emhoff提出的一些小問題；國會圖書館製作的片段；以及其他特別節目。

Defeat Predator Location (Predator Boss Fight) - Fortnite

For one of the Jungle Hunter Quests to unlock the Predator Skin in Fortnite Battle Royale, you need to "Defeat Predator".

You can find the Predator boss fight in Stealthy Stronghold, he spawns where the huts are at the back and will move about the area, invisible. Best way to defeat The Predator in Fortnite is to climb onto the shacks themselves, as he has difficulty getting you from up there.

Simply defeat Predator to complete this challenge and unlock the secret skin.

localize.title: 打败捕食者位置（捕食者BOSS战） - Fortnite
localize.description:
打败捕食者位置（捕食者BOSS战） - Fortnite

在《Fortnite大逃杀》中，要解锁Predator皮肤的丛林猎人任务之一，你需要 "击败Predator"。

你可以在Stealthy Stronghold中找到Predator的boss战，他在后面小木屋的地方产卵，会在这个区域移动，看不见。在Fortnite中击败Predator的最佳方法是自己爬到小屋上，因为他很难从上面抓到你。

只要击败Predator就可以完成这个挑战，解锁秘密皮肤。

localize.title: 打敗捕食者位置（捕食者BOSS戰） - Fortnite
localize.description:
打敗捕食者位置（捕食者BOSS戰） - Fortnite

在《Fortnite大逃殺》中，要解鎖Predator皮膚的叢林獵人任務之一，你需要 "擊敗Predator"。

你可以在Stealthy Stronghold中找到Predator的boss戰，他在後面小木屋的地方產卵，會在這個區域移動，看不見。在Fortnite中擊敗Predator的最佳方法是自己爬到小屋上，因爲他很難從上面抓到你。

只要擊敗Predator就可以完成這個挑戰，解鎖祕密皮膚。
